{
  "texts": [
    "There were no specific restrictions on study duration.",
    "Key search terms included \"Chatbot*\", \"conversational agent*\", \"virtual assistant\", \"artificial intelligence chatbot\", \"medical history\", and \"history-taking\".",
    "The quality of observational studies was classified using the STROBE criteria (e.g.",
    "sample size, design, data collection, follow-up).",
    "The RoB 2 tool assessed areas and the levels of bias in randomised clinical trials (RCTs)."
  ]
}